Package RestaurantSim.SimulationSystem

Class TickableAction

java.lang.Object
RestaurantSim.SimulationSystem.TickableAction
public class TickableAction
extends java.lang.Object
This class describes an action that spans some amount of ticks and also provides ways to define a behaviour on when this action is finished or is being updated. Every TickableAction has duration, can have a description and can be aborted at any time. Action can also be marked as repeatable, which means that action will be recreated when it is finished.
